Thanks for using gReader. With Premium membership you can extend your reading experience to a new level. Our goal is to make a simple, fast and intuitive app for reading news. With your support we can make gReader even better.
Get Premium for full content. You can also get Premium by watching a video.

App payments made through the Play Store are controlled and managed by Google. Your payment will be charged to your Play Store Account at confirmation of purchase. Your subscription automatically reviews unless auto-renew is turned off at lease 24 hours before the end of the current period. Your Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period., and the cost of the renewal will be stated. You may manage your subscriptions and may turn off auto-renewal by going to your Play Store Account Settings after purchase. You may cancel your purchase anytime during the 7-day trial period without cost, where applicable. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited if you purchase a subscription to that app, where applicable.
